description: Use Nexus as a integration point between Development and Operations
comments.comment: We're using Artifactory for same.; Having said that, our builds deploy to Artifactory but chef deploys from a Nexus mirror of that repository. It's complicated but no architects were hurt in the process.; Exactly how we do it at Post. The point being that unless you use this pattern you're not actually deploying the actual artifact that was tested.ï»¿ Dunno where this pattern fits into the new world of Docker though.
